public final class YaFormEditor
extends SimpleEditor
implements FormChangeListener

Editor for Young Android Form (.scm) files.

This editor shows a designer that provides support for visual design of forms.

Author:
markf@google.com (Mark Friedman), lizlooney@google.com (Liz Looney)
